    "Safety-Driven Validation: The prioritized nodes trigger realtime validation checks.",
    "For example:• If a mugâ Ȃ Źs temperature exceeds a safety threshold (e.g., > 85 • C), the EKG updates its node properties, and GATs increase its attention weight, forcing the robot to adjust its grip force or trajectory.",
    "• If a dynamic obstacle (e.g., a human) enters the robotâ Ȃ Źs path, the obstacleâ Ȃ Źs proximity feature updates, and GATs prioritize collision avoidance by rerouting the task plan within < 0.5s [12].",
    "To evaluate the safety compliance and task execution effectiveness of our proposed framework, we conducted a comprehensive set of experiments across two robotic platforms.",
    "Our evaluation includes comparisons between (i) ERCP + LLM for task plan generation and state-of-the-art LLMbased task planners, and (ii) EKG for real-time knowledgebased validation against traditional knowledge-based methods."
